      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DESTINI ORIETTA (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 16.73 beating EXHIBIT. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Can make it back-to-back wins. ALTONA BEACH (8) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (16.90) from Box 3 at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. NANDO WHIRLWIND (2) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when second beaten 2.25 lengths (16.83). Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Will give a great sight again. SOLAR FLARE (3) is building a nice sequence of wins and will be thereabouts again.",
